moa.streams.clustering

Class SimpleCSVStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • moa.AbstractMOAObject
      • moa.options.AbstractOptionHandler
        • moa.streams.clustering.ClusteringStream
          • moa.streams.clustering.SimpleCSVStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable, Serializable, MOAObject, OptionHandler, ExampleStream<Example<Instance>>, InstanceStream

    public class SimpleCSVStream
extends ClusteringStream
    Provides a simple input stream for csv files. Adds if necessary a class attribute with an identical default value.
